{"title":"windows下安装及配置Pycharm","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.033Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/windows下安装及配置Pycharm","updated":"2023-07-28T09:12:51.808Z","content":"<h2 id=\"1、下载pycharm\">1、<a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm/download/#section=windows\">下载pycharm</a><a title=\"#1、下载pycharm\" href=\"#1、下载pycharm\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b7e84f865a664a1a8ce18c4363f10a00.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n**</p>\n<h2 id=\"2、开始安装\">2、开始安装<a title=\"#2、开始安装\" href=\"#2、开始安装\"></a></h2>\n<p>**<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c052139fee2f49418b3cc3375f57cef8.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fa94df58070f4aff8e5d54079f332044.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/68e36b6d43cd41d397e47bf251b39b3d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/657b5ff5788c47e3bd9078bda4c2c154.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>等待安装</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a8b14c89f5074d0687ae6fa15ebf183a.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>结束安装<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/f8ca54c096434b51ba6be499ad4d637e.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件\">3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件<a title=\"#3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件\" href=\"#3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件\"></a></h2>\n<p>进入pycharm的bin目录，记事本打开<code>idea.properties</code>文件<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/99a39798bcc54aa98ac451af574d2de5.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>修改这两行<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/d9a064148eee43d5bbf12b962b28b1a6.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n删掉注释#<br>\n改成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">idea.config.path=../bin/path/config</span><br><span class=\"line\">idea.system.path=../bin/path/system</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/59035fcfc88f4730bd2296d6ebe6f7eb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n保存后,在<code>bin</code>目录下创建<code>path</code>文件夹<br>\n在<code>path</code>文件夹内创建<code>config</code>和<code>system</code>文件夹<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/93838b9ade0d41418fd136f7c8176d27.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Windows怎么把系统用户中文文件夹改成英文","link":"2023/07/28/Windows怎么把系统用户中文文件夹改成英文"},"next":{"title":"windows下的go语言环境安装","link":"2023/07/28/windows下的go语言环境安装"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/windows下安装及配置Pycharm/","toc":[{"id":"1、下载pycharm","title":"1、下载pycharm","index":"1"},{"id":"2、开始安装","title":"2、开始安装","index":"2"},{"id":"3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件","title":"3、接下来修改pycharm的配置文件","index":"3"}],"reading_time":"417 字约 3 分钟"}